===Proper noun===
'''iPod'''&reg; (''plural'' '''iPods''')
{{wikipedia}}
#A brand of [[MP3 player]] manufactured by [[w:Apple Computer|Apple Computer]] that stores [[media]] on either a small [[hard drive]] or [[flash memory]]

Etymology

''i'' - internet, from Apple Corporation's "i" line of products, originally used in iMac. Alternately, oneself - as in "I", or belonging to oneself.

''Pod'' - literally a pod, a place to keep things, consistent with the device's capability as a simple hard drive capable of storing anything (not just music)

